Just so you know, the idea is not terrible, and I like the concept of an SCP based on the Spanish Flu (Or at least that is what I believe it is). It is the execution that is the issue. The story lacks substance and seems to be a standard haunted building. The only nonstandard element is that it involves disease. If you focused more on the disease and the students themselves, then it could maybe have worked. As it is right now, -1.








